data.text:
Description

This Hong Kong business centre in Wheelock House sits atop the Central MTR Station and is minutes from 5-star hotels, shopping centres, international banks and all other important business services in core Hong Kong. With all the features, facilities and advantages of our larger centres, Wheelock House has been designed specifically to provide a premium, professional location for 1 to 24-person clients at an entry level price.The serviced offices and virtual office spaces at Wheelock House are equipped with the quality features you would expect from The Executive Centre.Cushioned by flexible leases at comfortable affordable prices your business is placed to succeed.
